import React from 'react';
import { Grid, Header, Button, Input, Feed } from 'semantic-ui-react';

class AutoNav extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
        <Grid Container id="autonav-page" centered columns={2}>
          <Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Column>
	      <Header as="h1" textAlign="center">AutoNav</Header>
            </Grid.Column>
            <Grid.Column>
	      <Header as="h1" textAlign="center">Indicator</Header>
            </Grid.Column>
          </Grid.Row>
          <Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Column>
	      <Header as="h1" textAlign="center">Queue List</Header>
	      <Feed>
    <Feed.Event
      image='/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg'
      content='You added Elliot Fu to the group Coworkers'
    />
    <Feed.Event>
      <Feed.Label image='../Images/rose-logo.png' />
      <Feed.Content content='You added Elliot Fu to the group Coworkers' />
    </Feed.Event>
  </Feed>
            </Grid.Column>
            <Grid.Column>
	      <Header as="h1" textAlign="center">Map</Header>
            </Grid.Column>
          </Grid.Row>
          <Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Column>
	      <Input action placeholder='X-Input' />
	      <Button type='submit'>Enter</Button>
            </Grid.Column>
            <Grid.Column>
	      <Input action placeholder='Y-Input' />
	      <Button type='submit'>Enter</Button>
            </Grid.Column>
          </Grid.Row>
        </Grid>
    );
  };
}

export default AutoNav;
